author: Ashwin Rodrigues, Leslie Horn
title: Nervous Rec: Watch Chris Gethard's Public Access Comedy Show
description: This show is a great rabbit hole and an accessible way to look at New York's up-and-coming comedy scene.
content: If you think rich people conferencing in from their second or third home is a bit unrelatable, a home-made version of Saturday Night Live or other late-night programs is not the balm you need to soothe your wounds from the chapping winds of reality. Instead, … [+2192 chars]
